Instrumentos de teste elétrico
Desde 1889, a Megger e suas empresas antecessoras têm ajudado engenheiros elétricos a manter a energia através do desenvolvimento e da fabricação de ferramentas portáteis para teste e medição.
Published: 15 September 2022
Download PDF
Elektrische testinstrumenten
Sinds 1889 ontwikkelt en produceert Megger, net als zijn voorgangers, draagbare test- en meetapparatuur waarmee elektrotechnici ononderbroken stroomvoorziening kunnen verzekeren.
Published: 15 September 2022
Download PDF
Strumenti per test elettrici [IT]
Strumenti per test elettrici
Published: 15 September 2022
Download PDF
Railway catalogue
Megger has partnered with several rail customers for many decades in developing and supplying test instrumentation to suit Rail applications. We continue to grow our product portfolio to compliment the rail industry and have recently added the Balto product testing range (page 9) to increase our HV breaker testing capabilities. Whether it’s specific test applications such as transformer testing, cable fault finding or more widely used general electrical test instruments, Megger is available to support you with your testing needs.
Published: 7 April 2022
